{
  "style": "IEEE",
  "texts": [
    "They developed a method to protect enterprise data, allowing companies to observe and analyse data flow and understand the reasons for data loss in realtime.",
    "In their analysis of the usage of ChatGPT by 1.6 million employees, they found that 3.1% of employees input internal company data directly into the AI for analysis.",
    "As the adoption of ChatGPT increased, so did the number of employees uploading enterprise data.",
    "In just one day (March 14), an average of 5267 instances of enterprise data were sent to ChatGPT per 100,000 employees.",
    "Of the corporate data sent directly to ChatGPT by employees, 11% was sensitive [27]."
  ],
